videos.description: Saquon Barkley takes the opening kickoff back 97 yards for a touchdown and Penn State takes an early lead.
videos.headline: Barkley returns opening kickoff 97 yards for TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Barkley returns opening kickoff 97 yards for TD) 2017/10/28 ESHEET

videos.description: The Nittany Lions take a 14-0 lead on the Buckeyes in the first quarter as DaeSean Hamilton catches a 13-yard TD pass from Trace McSorley.
videos.headline: McSorley finds Hamilton to extend Penn State's lead

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McSorley finds Hamilton to extend Penn State's lead) 2017/10/28 ESHEET

videos.description: Saquon Barkley breaks loose for a 36-yard rushing touchdown that extends Penn State's lead in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: Barkley scores 2nd TD on 36-yard run

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Barkley scores 2nd TD on 36-yard run) 2017/10/28 ESHEET

videos.description: J.T. Barrett connects with WR Terry McLaurin for a 14-yard Ohio State touchdown, cutting Penn State's lead to 21-10.
videos.headline: Barrett throws 1st Ohio State TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Barrett throws 1st Ohio State TD) 2017/10/28 ESHEET

videos.description: Trace McSorley calls his own number and finds the end zone from 6 yards out to extend the Nittany Lions' lead in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: McSorley's scores Penn State's fourth TD of half

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McSorley's scores Penn State's fourth TD of half) 2017/10/28 ESHEET

videos.description: Mike Weber scores on a 2-yard rushing TD that chips away at the Buckeyes' deficit in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: Buckeyes trim lead on Weber's TD run

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buckeyes trim lead on Weber's TD run) 2017/10/28 ESHEET

videos.description: No. 2 Penn State scores 28 first-half points, the most allowed by Ohio State since the 2007 BCS Championship (vs. Urban Meyer's Florida team).
videos.headline: Penn State dominant in first half from Columbus

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Penn State dominant in first half from Columbus) 2017/10/28 SOTFULL ESHEET

videos.description: Trace McSorley flings it 37 yards to the end zone where DeAndre Thompkins battles Denzel Ward for the catch. The original call of an interception was overturned to a touchdown, increasing Penn State's lead over Ohio State.
videos.headline: PSU's Thompkins fights for 37-yard TD catch

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (PSU's Thompkins fights for 37-yard TD catch) 2017/10/28 ESHEET

videos.description: J.T. Barrett finds Johnnie Dixon over the middle for a 38-yard touchdown that trims Ohio State's deficit in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Barrett finds Dixon for 38-yard score

videos.description: J.T. Barrett throws right to Johnnie Dixon for a 10-yard touchdown that brings Ohio State within five in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Barrett hits Dixon for clutch TD
